com.github.bwsoft.iris.message

Enum FieldType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<FieldType>
      • com.github.bwsoft.iris.message.FieldType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<FieldType>

    public enum FieldType
extends java.lang.Enum<FieldType>
    Defines all supported types. The size is defined as the number of bytes that requires to hold this field. A size of zero indicates the size of the field is determined dynamically.
    Author:
    yzhou
